# Build after CSS/JS changes

This project serves **minified** CSS and JS (`styles.min.css`, `script.min.js`). The HTML references those files.

**After editing any of these files**, run:

```bash
npm run build
```

so that the minified outputs are updated. Otherwise the site will not reflect your changes until you build.

**Files that require a build after change:**
- `assets/css/styles.css`
- `assets/js/script.js`
